text: Dr. Marie Zdeňka Baborová-Čiháková (17 January 1877, Prague - 29 September 1937, Čelákovice) was the first female Czech botanist and zoologist. ==Works== * ==See also== *Timeline of women in science ==References== Category:1877 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Czech women scientists Category:Czech botanists Category:Czech zoologists Category:Women botanists
